@startuml
title Post-Phase Backlog Focus

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "P0 User Surface" {
  [Issue Detail Git Card]
  [Merge Candidate Card]
}

package "Current Runtime" {
  [Protocol Artifacts]
  [Workspace Git Snapshot]
  [Isolated Worktree]
  [Verification Signals]
}

package "P1 Operations" {
  [Nightly Real-Org E2E]
  [Prompt Quality Tightening]
}

package "P2/P3 RAG" {
  [RAG Metrics]
  [Cross-Project Retrieval]
  [Deep RAG Hardening]
}

[Isolated Worktree] --> [Workspace Git Snapshot]
[Isolated Worktree] --> [Verification Signals]
[Verification Signals] --> [Protocol Artifacts]
[Workspace Git Snapshot] --> [Issue Detail Git Card]
[Protocol Artifacts] --> [Issue Detail Git Card]
[Workspace Git Snapshot] --> [Merge Candidate Card]
[Protocol Artifacts] --> [Merge Candidate Card]

[Nightly Real-Org E2E] --> [Issue Detail Git Card]
[Nightly Real-Org E2E] --> [Merge Candidate Card]
[Nightly Real-Org E2E] --> [RAG Metrics]

[RAG Metrics] --> [Cross-Project Retrieval]
[Cross-Project Retrieval] --> [Deep RAG Hardening]

note right of [Issue Detail Git Card]
Show branch, worktree, changed files,
diff stat, test/build artifacts,
and review evidence.
end note

note right of [Merge Candidate Card]
Bridge pending_external_merge
to operator approval and
later PR/merge automation.
end note

@enduml
